{"tid":924399,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB引消息：免差餉致庫房少收廿億 擬限每業主僅一單位獲寬免","createTime":"2018-12-02T05:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T07:32:35.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5eecfef205a5fbcb80acec6bfcbbe91eec5d6c6a","tid":924399,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T05:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181201/large/1543662505_5703.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181201%2Flarge%2F1543662505_5703.jpg&h=a69a4515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n財政預算案近年「派糖」措施，多數包括寬免差餉，但現時有關寬免未有限制可獲差餉寬免的物業數量，即若一名業主同時持有多個物業，可以所有物業都獲得差餉寬免。TVB今日《六點半新聞》引述消息指，庫房每年因此少收約20億元差餉，明年2月公佈的新一份財政預算案，可能會修改現有的寬免機制。<br />\n<br />\nTVB引消息指，鑒於公平原則，港府有意改動機制，限制每名業主或公司，只能以名下其中一個物業接受差餉寬免。估計減少多重優惠下，政府庫房可進帳約20億元差餉。同時，由於改變機制後需要增聘人手及添置電腦等，預料成本超過2億。換言之，若政府改動機制，有機會進帳近18億元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181201/58981136\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181201%2F58981136&d=SjzH5d%2B%2FsKn5MNMwa28LvpUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=c1b4ef6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181201%2F58981136&h=78f8a30d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181201/58981136</a>"},{"pid":"78abdbb9c7f11d7fe72a640f7eedfde8ba0acc58","tid":924399,"uid":21052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T05:54:57.000Z","msg":"消息指"},{"pid":"b0e51c7a8db93e169a97f980e12d81762c9668d1","tid":924399,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T07:20:55.000Z","msg":"差餉已經係政府對全港物業收嘅服務費，收差餉仲要另搞垃圾收費，搞雙重壓榨同利益輸送。"},{"pid":"c7e0f069cd1c758f57f617816fb8022c0782d8b0","tid":924399,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78abdbb9c7f11d7fe72a640f7eedfde8ba0acc58","tid":924399,"uid":21052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T05:54:57.000Z","msg":"消息指"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T07:22:01.000Z","msg":"據知情人士透露"},{"pid":"3827c020c1f8541b5f047d0f201eb08f59574460","tid":924399,"uid":18955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T07:23:44.000Z","msg":"應該primary residence 先可以免"},{"pid":"45f9d22c690071c06d109d68c5cdf57d6560772e","tid":924399,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T07:24:39.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n我租舖就慘<br />\n又要硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79dd0c41d460c3aef001c7d69924bd0f08eebc4","tid":924399,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T07:25:28.000Z","msg":"交差餉俾差佬"},{"pid":"c9d89ba06637b9ff8bc23d77449d2e7a37f916af","tid":924399,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T07:25:29.000Z","msg":"一早應該啦"},{"pid":"96a8b9af2084980d20a0388aad88f0c44af8669a","tid":924399,"uid":1550,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T07:32:35.000Z","msg":"有兩間以上應該一個單位都唔好寬免<br />\n有錢買樓冇錢比差餉"}]}